# {VENDOR_DISPLAY} API credentials
# Copy this file to .secrets and fill in your values.
# Set permissions: chmod 640, chown root:wazuh
#
# Lines starting with # are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
# Values may be single or double quoted.

# CUSTOMIZE: Replace with your vendor's credential variable names
# {VENDOR_UPPER}_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
# {VENDOR_UPPER}_API_SECRET=your-api-secret-here
